# ============================================================================
# GitHub Copilot Content Exclusion Rules (.copilotignore)
# ============================================================================
# This file reduces embedding load and improves Copilot Chat performance by
# excluding files that are not useful for context generation.
#
# Best Practices:
# - Exclude generated/compiled code (not human-written)
# - Exclude binary files and large assets
# - Exclude dependency directories (node_modules, vendor, etc.)
# - Exclude logs, caches, and temporary files
# - Exclude secrets and sensitive configuration
# ============================================================================

# ============================================================================
# DEPENDENCY DIRECTORIES - Largest impact on performance
# ============================================================================
